title: Tejaswi Yadav interview: ‘BJP is anti-development, everyone knows it’
text: Tejaswi Yadav interview: ‘BJP is anti-development, everyone knows it’ Thursday, 15 October 2015 (20 minutes ago) Lalu Prasad's youngest son Tejaswi speaks to Sheela Bhatt about 'jungle raj', his father's 'involvement' in the fodder scam, and how he plans on changing the face of Bihar.
